Hi, I'm playing with a lot of part mods, and when I filter parts by size I saw some parts have duplicates sometimes even with different stats, I can still see Restock+ parts that are hidden when Making History installed, also some of the eve optimized engines doesn't show up(atleast when I tried search for parts from that mod). For example, the Boa engine is in the engine list when I filter by function, the Asp engine is only in the part list when I filter by part size, but both parts can't be found by searching.

Is there some part confict going on?

And if the mod set is fine, I will look for these parts more carefully.

Edited February 28, 2020 by Space Nerd

Maybe similar to this old I issue I had a while ago?

Turned out, the search gave me both, the original, and the modified part.
